tional genomics to improve animal health, setting the scene for the day. The workshop identified several aims including identifying pipelines and sharing methods within bioinformatics applicable to comparative and veterinary immune research. Applications of studying bioinformatics in veterinary vaccinology were highlighted:
?response to vaccination v natural infection
